{"tid":701161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃世柒﹕人民幣 啲貨幣基礎開始亂咁嚟","createTime":"2018-06-14T02:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T17:40:24.000Z","uid":141151,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f0195cc069770eebbacff756863cfe0aab56fb26","tid":701161,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T02:13:40.000Z","msg":"人民幣 啲貨幣基礎開始亂咁嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/19689/%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3-%E5%95%B2%E8%B2%A8%E5%B9%A3%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B%E4%BA%82%E5%92%81%E5%9A%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F19689%2F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25A3-%25E5%2595%25B2%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E5%25B9%25A3%25E5%259F%25BA%25E7%25A4%258E%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25A7%258B%25E4%25BA%2582%25E5%2592%2581%25E5%259A%259F&d=jSaVrvWmoXwvmhgKSppV07%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=7ef40c4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/19689/%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3-%E5%95%B2%E8%B2%A8%E5%B9%A3%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B%E4%BA%82%E5%92%81%E5%9A%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家用個腦簡單諗吓就明，依家有間地方企業，盤數化妝到好靚，AA級債，跟住間企業用自己公司債券做抵押，問銀行借錢，銀行再攞債券向人民銀行抵押借錢放數，中間賺息，跟住間地方企業執咗，老闆走佬去美國，然後留低一堆爛帳無人找，問題嚟，咁果啲抵押品點算，人民銀行自己食咗啲損失，定問銀行call loan，問銀行call loan，就銀行有危機，人民銀行自己食咗損失佢，就結果印咗堆無資產擔保下印出嚟嘅人民幣周街走，咁人民幣幣值係會出大事。</span>"},{"pid":"48889a28a35ae79adce15ad80c2b8a852f37f6f0","tid":701161,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T02:15:59.000Z","msg":"幾號支爆？"},{"pid":"596a6c0bc54c0e0ac20639ef68bb741d1fca2a01","tid":701161,"uid":25858,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T02:23:23.000Z","msg":"coming soon <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ebbe3b6962a022c6a381ca9d2190eaddd4fa95a","tid":701161,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T03:05:48.000Z","msg":"所以大陸樓價又可以gogogo<br />\n變相香港樓抵買又gogogo"},{"pid":"85